Simple Comparison Table
----------------------

| Optimizer | Speed      | Popularity | Best Use               |
| --------- | ---------- | ---------- | ---------------------- |
| SGD       | Slow       | Medium     | Basic learning         |
| RMSprop   | Medium     | High       | RNN                    |
| Adam      | Fast       | Very High  | Most projects          |
| AdamW     | Fast       | Very High  | Transformers           |
| Adadelta  | Medium     | Medium     | Auto LR                |
| Adagrad   | Slow later | Medium     | NLP                    |
| Adamax    | Fast       | Low        | Special cases          |
| Adafactor | Fast       | High       | Large models           |
| Nadam     | Fast       | Medium     | Smooth training        |
| Ftrl      | Medium     | Medium     | Recommendation systems |


